{"type":"markdown","params":{"markdown":"#### **Data will only be visible in this dashboard if you enable the Flow_TopLevelDomain system rule.**
* A **Top Level Domain (TLD)** is the highest level domain name. For example, "com" is the TLD of https://support.logrhythm.com. Domain_TLD_NM will be "com".
* A **Second Level Domain (SLD)** is the second highest level domain name. For example, "logrhythm" is the SLD of https://support.logrhythm.com. Domain_SLD_NM will be "logrhythm.com".
* A **Fully Qualified Domain Name (FQDN)** is the full domain after the application. For example, "support.logrhythm.com" is the FQDN of https://support.logrhythm.com. Domain_FQDN_NM will be "support.logrhythm.com"."},"aggs":[],"listeners":{}}
